						<div class="weather-icon">🌀</div>
						<h3>Variable Wind Patterns</h3>
						<p><strong>Challenge:</strong> Seasonal winds and occasional strong weather fronts</p>
						<p><strong>Our Solution:</strong> Enhanced post depths, wind-load engineering, flexible panel connections</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="weather-factor">
						<div class="weather-icon">💧</div>
						<h3>Clay Soil Movement</h3>
